---
title: Bruschetta Chicken Tenders Salad with Croutons and Parmesan
description: We've taken the flavours of a classic Italian antipasto and made it into a delicious meal for the whole family! Crunchy croutons are tossed with spring mix, juicy tomatoes and fresh basil for a burst of flavour. It's all topped with creamy Parmesan and a final drizzle of balsamic glaze.
